1. Installed Node.js using NVM (Node Version Manager)
   Command: curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Restarted the terminal to activate NVM

3. Installed Node.js version 20.16
   Command: nvm install 20.16

4. Installed Sass using npm
   Command: npm install sass@1.37.4

